jquery.name: jQuery
jquery.description: jQuery is a fast, small, and feature-rich JavaScript library. It makes things like HTML document traversal and manipulation, event handling, animation, and Ajax much simpler with an easy-to-use API that works across a multitude of browsers.

jquery-ui.name: jQuery UI
jquery-ui.description: jQuery UI is a curated set of user interface interactions, effects, widgets, and themes built on top of the jQuery JavaScript Library

ace.name: Ace
ace.description: Ace is a code editor written in JavaScript.
